For publication purposes, the indicators can be grouped by categories of ICT products into the following groups: 
1. Computer and peripheral equipment; 
2. Communication equipment (telecommunication equipment); 
3. Household electronic appliances (audio and video equipment);
4. Other components of ICT products.

